c: 40
v: 29
t: "You my nation, for you (is) the kingdom/ownership the day/today, conquering/defeating in the earth/Planet Earth, so who gives us victory/aid from God`s courage/might/power, if (it) came to us? Pharaoh said: \"I do not show you/make you understand except what I see/understand, and I do not guide you except the corrects/right guidance`s way/path"